This directory contains information about the product.
Documentation can be found here:
http://en.opensuse.org/Build_Service/Concepts/Product_Definition

The directory should be added to the concerning build repository with the name 
"_product". The buildservice creates the concerning packages automatically.

You can also check the syntax and build the packages with following steps:

Installing OBS
-------------------
Add repo
- - - - - - - 

zypper ar http://download.opensuse.org/repositories/openSUSE:/Tools:/Unstable/openSUSE_11.2/ obs

Install needed packages
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -

zypper in obs-productconverter

Generating spec and KIWI file
--------------------------------------

/usr/lib/obs/server/bs_productconvert sle-11-SP1-WebYaST.product  /tmp/sle-11-SP1-WebYaST

Building
-----------

check out Devel:WebYaST

go to Devel:WebYaST/_product:sle-11-WebYaST-cd-cd-i586_x86_64

osc build images i586
